iness/international-business/economic-fury-on-iran-us-seizes-tehrans-biggest-crypto-network-amid-peace-talks/articleshow/131474989.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-03T09:47:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Business Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131475577,imgsize-2683171.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Air defence battle over Kuwait as Patriot missiles respond to Iranian strike]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131474698.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Middle East tensions flared as Iran launched missiles targeting US facilities in Kuwait and Bahrain, which were intercepted or failed to hit. The US responded with strikes on an Iranian military site. This escalation follows a major US military campaign against Iran earlier this year, with ongoing exchanges and stalled negotiations pushing the region towards wider conflict.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/watch-air-defence-battle-over-kuwait-as-patriot-missiles-respond-to-iranian-strike/articleshow/131474698.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/watch-air-defence-battle-over-kuwait-as-patriot-missiles-respond-to-iranian-strike/articleshow/131474698.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-03T09:21:02+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131474682,imgsize-1124968.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Bitcoin is garbage": Clavicular's brutal Bitcoin takedown sparks outrage and mockery across crypto world]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131473544.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Controversial streamer Clavicular sparked widespread backlash after calling Bitcoin "garbage" and a "horrible investment" during a viral livestream. He argued that the cryptocurrency lacks intrinsic value and claimed its biggest gains are already behind it. His comments drew criticism from crypto supporters, who defended Bitcoin's growing institutional adoption and long-term potential. The rant also revived discussions about Clavicular's past disagreements with fellow streamer Sneako and previous crypto-related controversies.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/bitcoin-is-garbage-claviculars-brutal-bitcoin-takedown-sparks-outrage-and-mockery-across-crypto-world/articleshow/131473544.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/bitcoin-is-garbage-claviculars-brutal-bitcoin-takedown-sparks-outrage-and-mockery-across-crypto-world/articleshow/131473544.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-03T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131473544,imgsize-420604.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is LowTierGod? Dale Wilson turns heads with rare court victory amid alleged doxxing dispute]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131473418.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[LowTierGod, whose real name is Dale Wilson, is trending after reportedly winning a California family court case without a lawyer. Wilson received a three-year restraining order against the mother of his child over alleged harassment and sharing of personal information. The court outcome sparked major discussion across social media, with fans and critics debating the surprising legal victory.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-lowtiergod-dale-wilson-turns-heads-with-rare-court-victory-amid-alleged-doxxing-dispute/articleshow/131473418.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-lowtiergod-dale-wilson-turns-heads-with-rare-court-victory-amid-alleged-doxxing-dispute/articleshow/131473418.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-03T03:59:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131473414,imgsize-893037.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[LowTierGod reportedly secures restraining order against mother of his child]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131471185.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Fighting game streamer LowTierGod has reportedly secured a restraining order against the mother of his child following a civil court hearing. Despite attending without legal representation, the streamer convinced the judge of harassment and unwanted contact. The order's specifics remain undisclosed, but the ruling has sparked significant online discussion within the gaming community.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/lowtiergod-reportedly-secures-restraining-order-against-mother-of-his-child/articleshow/131471185.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/lowtiergod-reportedly-secures-restraining-order-against-mother-of-his-child/articleshow/131471185.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-03T02:08:29+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131471187,imgsize-554386.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian man to be deported from New Zealand after being caught in underage sex ring, says he would face stigma back home]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspac